    b"e task-relevant guidance.\x0a        - Keep task_input concise and natural. Use lig"
    b"ht bullets when they make it\x0a          easier to read.\x0a        - Write for the t"
    b"ask runner using human-meaningful context rather than\x0a          source bookkeepi"
    b"ng.\x0a        - Set candidate_memory only when this composition step reveals durab"
    b"le\x0a          guidance for future prompt composition.\x0a        - Keep a list of ex"
    b"act memories when their contents as memories are directly related to the user re"
    b"quest.\x0a        - When keeping exact memories make sure to keep their parent cont"
    b"ext memory as well so the structure/origin of the memory is kept even if its sib"
    b"lings aren't.\x0a\x0a        {{ _.role(\"user\") }}\x0a\x0a        Selected task prompt:\x0a     "
